item.title: Nikita Ostapenco
item.description: I discovered a Moldovan artist named Nikita Ostapenco while shopping for a secret Santa gift for a co-worker. Check out their art! Lots of amazing colors, and interesting characters and backgrounds! https://www.artfinder.com/artist/ostapenconikita/
